</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

</section>
<section id="slide-orgb6d3066" data-background="../../images/SLIDE-WIDE_BG-blue_SmlLogo-top-right.png" data-background-size="cover" data-background-opacity="1">
<h3 id="orgb6d3066">3.2 Examples of prefixes</h3>
<table border="2" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="6" rules="groups" frame="hsides" class="fragment (roll-in) ;frag_idx (1)" style="text-align:left">


